## 🛠 Usage Tips for GitHub
* **Variable Consistency**: Ensure you define your variables once in the "Research Content" section to keep the AI from hallucinating different symbols ($P_{gen}$ vs $P_g$).
* **Batch Processing**: Use the **Master Control Prompt** first to set the persona, then feed specific sections using the sub-prompts.
